{"tid":2256182,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［求廣傳］獄中手足寫比香港人既家書","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T03:05:04.000Z","uid":69472,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"da84c54ff2f324ca9ed7e42f82d3f1cfff8cf000","tid":2256182,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"前文提要：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">[求廣傳］獄中手足寫左12頁信畀我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2211303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2211303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得呢位還押左近一年既手足？<br />\n佢又寫左新一批既信比我地，<br />\n佢仍然都係咁堅強，喺惡劣既環境下仍有十分堅定既意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次佢既信有成43頁咁多，佢一直好想有多啲人一齊睇佢既信，唔知各位巴絲會唔會都會成為呢位手足既讀者？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣，有班好熱心既港人幫手譯左佢既信做英文，<br />\n可以喺呢度睇到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WalkWithHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWalkWithHK%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=df233cf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WalkWithHK/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCQsyXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCQsyXK.jpg&h=498a9e77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FT544q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FT544q.jpg&h=73dc74c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjY9NhM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjY9NhM.jpg&h=b38bcf31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFnVHQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFnVHQ7.jpg&h=59f9d147&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rd0cK4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frd0cK4t.jpg&h=70774726&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zySuNhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzySuNhP.jpg&h=a6f93a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYTJRKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYTJRKu.jpg&h=5cf0c9df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1g0L44w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1g0L44w.jpg&h=6ccc5b25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qpd544x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpd544x.jpg&h=4a576b27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PGfHRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PGfHRd.jpg&h=bd495bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"42d10b5b88c28257f1ce7bb83ccad18e48cbb861","tid":2256182,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a780cbe93402b09ff9cdb288290bacbda054dca6","tid":2256182,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1f1ebbd62a08e9a90babe9251174ebbd203ac4","tid":2256182,"uid":241331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"字好靚"},{"pid":"113ad44121f951f07572175e267f8b4322826149","tid":2256182,"uid":69472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LyRfHUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyRfHUR.jpg&h=c9198b56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95yJROc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95yJROc.jpg&h=25c296e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDiRgeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?